Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.24,0:00:05.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, two letters came for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.30,0:00:08.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:10.23,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:13.71,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama-san, you wear contacts?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.54,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:20.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot I was still dressed like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.27,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:23.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:25.60,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nanamin, you look cute with glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:26.82,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see you! Let me see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:30.34,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No, Senpai! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:32.66,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We're both girls, so what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.29,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What are those letters about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:34.40,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:34.76,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:37.35,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No! The boys are watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:35.53,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda Sorata-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:37.09,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's Make a Game!" Screening Committee Member
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:38.77,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Then, should we continue this in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:39.96,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe in the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.96,0:00:40.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:43.12,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do it outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:43.73,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:46.38,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You need some surprises in your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:49.15,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,No surprises, no life!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:49.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:52.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I passed the first screening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:54.76,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}"Let's Make a Game!"{\b0}\NInstructions for Candidates Who Have \NPassed the Initial Screening Process
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They want me to go and do \Na presentation on the 31st!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:55.95,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:57.24,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:58.70,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,He did it, Nanamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:00:59.99,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're so soft, Nanamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:00.02,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:02.74,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:01.27,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:02.80,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's in the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:17.47,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.50,0:01:16.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}is{\i0} this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:20.76,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about love?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:57.53,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}Teach me about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:59.51,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1200,400)}#08 Set Off a Huge Firework
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:00.46,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.17,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me about love (koi).
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.06,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me about love (koi).
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:09.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Koi are freshwater fish \Nthat live in lakes and rivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:12.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The value of decorative koi \Ndepends on their markings,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.87,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and expensive ones can \Ngo for millions of yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:15.59,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't! You actually \Nwanted to learn about fish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:18.96,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.71,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Make my heart pound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:23.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that so nonchalantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.97,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Make my chest tighten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't handle such huge responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:27.54,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} try showing some fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why are you suddenly \Nso interested in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:33.06,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ayano told me:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:37.67,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,"The best way to learn how to write \Nabout love is by falling in love."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:41.53,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,She said that anyone could write \None love story in their lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Your editor doesn't have any trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:46.37,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,coming out with embarrassing \Nstatements, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:50.43,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There's a meeting to pick out new \Nserializations on the 31st.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:52.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The 31st?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:54.83,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I've got a \Npresentation that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:04:00.30,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,Instructions for Pitch Presentations\N for the Second Stage of Screening
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:56.19,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,A presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:58.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,My presentation for the "Let's \NMake a Game!" competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I passed the initial screening, \Nso I need to prepare for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.34,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:05.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They're both on the same day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:06.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.77,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a boy's room \Nwithout pants on again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:13.91,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:14.60,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.67,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:19.22,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Because boys are perverted creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:21.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act as though I represent all boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.78,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.48,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. I still haven't\N learned about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:29.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You saw this, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:32.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina's editor told her to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:35.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that doesn't mean \Nmistakes won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:36.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What am I, a brute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:37.31,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:37.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.86,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun has to prepare \Nfor his presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:40.97,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get in his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:42.46,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not bothering him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:46.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I mean, she isn't \Ngetting in my way, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:46.89,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's not bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:52.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:54.72,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to \Npick a fight with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:56.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not picking a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.26,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:02.20,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's going \Nto fight kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:05.62,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I think pudding is a beverage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:07.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,At least stay on topic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:12.58,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, that's why pudding \Nshakes are evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.01,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:19.88,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, do you know about love?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:27.57,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata-sama has logged on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:37.90,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata-sama has logged on.\N{\b1}Kanda Sorata: {\b0}Akasaka, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:37.90,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}Maid-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:32.37,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke-sama is currently \Ndeep in contemplation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:35.64,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,about what would happen if \Nyou opened both doors...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.90,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,of a two-door refrigerator\N at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:42.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see. In that case, \Nyou'll do, Maid-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:45.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any advice on \Nhow to do a presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:53.68,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you'll do, Maid-chan.\NDo you have any advice on \Nhow to do a presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:53.68,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}Maid-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:48.94,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,How should I punish you \Nto death for suggesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:52.02,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that anyone would do (lol)?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:53.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You answered your own question!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.08,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke:{\b0} Wear a suit. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're there suddenly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:06:00.31,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke:{\b0} Also, practice your presentation \Nskills with the residents of Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:03.32,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke:{\b0} Also, practice your presentation \Nskills with the residents of Sakura Hall.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Fortunately, you have plenty of \Nunique individuals here to test them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:05.05,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke:{\b0} Also, practice your presentation \Nskills with the residents of Sakura Hall.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Fortunately, you have plenty of \Nunique individuals here to test them on.\N{\b1}Ryunosuke-sama has logged off.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.34,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.44,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let the training begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.35,Sign,BANNER,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun Training
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, due to this system, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that it wouldn't \Njust be core users...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:28.61,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who'd enjoy this game; it would \Nattract a lot of new players, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:31.02,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,20 minutes, 53 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.14,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:37.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I tried using Fujisawa Kazuki's \Naward-winning pitch as a template.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:41.93,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Explain it so there's clear progression \Nfrom introduction through conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.44,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're not acting like your usual self,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.21,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's not interesting at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.67,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Your choice of words \Nis a little awkward, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.70,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're including too many elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.85,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's hard to tell what \Nyour main point is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try improving it tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:08.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to it again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.37,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,He's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.29,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:15.99,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,If it goes well, Nanamin says \Nshe'll give you a kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.69,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.07,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,On the cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:22.17,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Where isn't the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,My concept is simple and fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:34.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, simple as well as...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, exhilarating...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:40.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina, what are you doing in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:42.31,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Designing characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing that in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:49.33,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,If I do it here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:50.90,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'll understand \Nwhat it means to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:55.02,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Should I leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.79,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:01.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If Aoyama finds you, she'll be annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.42,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:05.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.51,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You always think of Nanami first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:12.93,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:15.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:44.12,Sign,NOTE,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:43.23,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The sun rose and set again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:50.21,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,After rewriting my presentation, \NI made everyone listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:53.27,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and then, I'd rewrite it \Nand practice again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.14,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Red Brick Road Shopping District
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:09:00.40,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,After repeating the \Nprocess ten times...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:04.04,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I greeted the morning \Nof my decisive battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:08.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:10.26,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.28,Sign,CHARM,0000,0000,0000,,Victory
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:16.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.32,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I went yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:18.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,With who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:23.41,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I looked it up, asked some\N people, and walked a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Did you go by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:30.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. You'll find out if your work's \Ngoing to be serialized today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.96,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:35.30,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:40.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.82,Sign,PAPER,0000,0000,0000,,Entry: Kanda Sorata
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.82,Sign,PAPER,0000,0000,0000,,School/Employment: Suimei University of the Arts
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:03.20,Saku-main,EXAMINER,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda Sorata-san, please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a pleasure to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.59,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Fujisawa Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.00,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:24.60,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,before we jump into your presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:25.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:30.40,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you need \Nto do to become a creator?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:35.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um... w-well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:40.67,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I need to tell him something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:42.33,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:46.04,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:48.87,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:53.58,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,My mind's gone blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:58.34,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Evening Fireworks Display\NStarts Today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:12.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,N-Next, um... u-uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.68,Saku-main,FISH,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're Kanda's kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:18.97,Saku-main,FISH,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the getup?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:21.20,Saku-main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking sharp. \NAre you going on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:27.22,Saku-main,FISH,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.66,Saku-main,EXAMINER,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda Sorata-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:33.14,Saku-main,EXAMINER,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:36.34,Saku-main,EXAMINER,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:44.90,Saku-main,EXAMINER,0000,0000,0000,,I regret to inform you that \Nyour pitch has been rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.29,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.32,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:23.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How did the meeting go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:26.74,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be serialized \Nstarting in November's issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:27.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:29.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.28,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:34.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'd better start drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:36.11,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Please go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:37.74,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:39.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stay here. Go draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.32,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Please go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.85,0:12:42.59,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:43.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:46.74,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:51.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the way forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:54.92,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:16.69,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,He was rejected, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:20.11,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not an easy world to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:22.44,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,He was prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:30.66,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried about \Nhim, Nanamin? Kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:31.78,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.04,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.00,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's throw a welcome \Nparty for Aoyama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:36.82,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:39.06,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I agree! Good idea, Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:41.55,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:42.14,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! Why would you suggest that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:44.38,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the only day it could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.22,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I've got just the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.39,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I've been \Nsaving for a special occasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.93,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It'll start at six! Everybody had better be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.32,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:52.72,Sign,PAPER,0000,0000,0000,,Presentation Materials
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:00.11,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}"Let's Make a Game!"{\b0}\NInstructions for Candidates Who Have \NPassed the Initial Screening Process
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:10.20,Sign,BOX,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure Chest
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:11.70,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:18.25,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:20.29,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:23.14,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The fateful day mankind \Nhas been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:26.70,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, which one do you like best?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:29.31,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.25,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding. They're swimsuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:31.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:35.65,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Why's your reaction so different \Nfor underwear and swimsuits?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:36.50,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Stop thinking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:41.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you scattering \Nswimsuits all over my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:44.73,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I figured we could have a pool \Nparty to welcome Nanamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.95,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:51.93,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Me, Nanamin, Mashiron and I will \Nall be waiting for you in our swimsuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:52.91,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:56.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned yourself \Ntwice, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:59.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, are pools even \Nopen at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.53,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're forgetting the school pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:02.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're not suggesting \Nwe sneak in, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.11,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! Jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:06.80,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I ran the idea by Chihiro-chan, \Nso there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:07.88,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,...said it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:09.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:10.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:13.34,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a welcome party...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:13.34,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:15.63,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick one out for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:18.19,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Or would you rather I chose for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:20.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:23.91,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We're throwing a welcome \Npool party for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:24.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:25.95,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nanamin, which one do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:27.32,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun said he likes this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:28.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:28.50,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:30.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's not me you're \Nsupposed to be fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Your enemy is this alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.07,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You should go with a string bikini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mitaka-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.28,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.43,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough from both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:38.79,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even said I'm \Ngoing yet. Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:41.50,Sign,PAPER,0000,0000,0000,,Presentation Materials
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.79,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and clear these away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:48.67,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.71,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Nanamin and kouhai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:54.42,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No. School starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:56.02,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:58.64,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We can't end our summer vacation \Nwithout wearing swimsuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.46,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:01.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.02,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:09.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to Aoyama's \Nwelcome pool party!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:15.53,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is calling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.14,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:20.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You should warm up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Aoyama and Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:24.42,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,They should be done changing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:30.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, how do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.17,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Too plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:34.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mitaka-senpai, I'm not asking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:35.51,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.31,0:16:38.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:40.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I think you look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:42.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:51.86,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I know it's not as bold as \NKamiigusa-senpai's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.89,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the most I can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:56.70,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time \Nwearing anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.94,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what I'd \Ndo if I looked all weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:01.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, it looks really good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're speaking with\N a Kansai accent again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:03.87,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:11.21,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:13.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.11,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.43,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You complimented Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:23.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. It looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.14,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:25.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:44.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:49.05,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:51.00,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kickboard cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kanda-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:58.30,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:03.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.16,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Aoyama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.31,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's jump in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:10.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:11.02,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:22.49,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Killer Niagara Tub Falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:24.77,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Let me practice my aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:27.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:29.16,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to cover \Nanything, cover your boobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:29.91,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:30.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get it undone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:35.17,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I declare this territory \NKouhai-kun Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.17,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Give them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.17,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That was terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:39.13,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:41.30,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Pool parties are all about \Nwardrobe malfunctions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.08,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}No nip slip, no life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:43.87,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You brought this all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:45.19,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Come on, kouhai-kun! Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:47.41,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have a Sakura Hall \Nwelcome party without hotpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:48.39,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Curry-flavored.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:54.36,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you kids doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:55.70,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:56.53,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,That was quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:59.36,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mitaka-senpai, you said \Nyou got permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:01.37,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way the school would \Ngive us permission to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:02.13,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:02.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:04.31,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Just hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:05.37,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go change!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.54,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where'd you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:09.21,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:14.35,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,You pool thieves! \NSplish, splash, making a racket!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:16.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:20.32,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move, Kanda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:21.77,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Shush, quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:24.34,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, don't look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:25.50,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move, Shiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:32.44,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,A new charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:36.23,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The embroidery is prettier \Nthan the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:37.40,Sign,CHARM,0000,0000,0000,,Easy Delivery
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:47.43,Sign,CHARM,0000,0000,0000,,Easy Delivery
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.09,0:19:50.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.72,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:02.43,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be sadder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:08.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I am sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.01,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,They're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:15.73,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:36.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:41.30,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop running, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:48.09,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That man has a scary look on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:48.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.08,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,You kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:52.40,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,You're from Sakura Hall, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:55.76,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoying your youth with \Nno regard for anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:57.69,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:16.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:18.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:21.82,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You can cry, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:24.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I won't cry. I'm not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.63,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's your problem? \NI'm just trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Being all serious about \Nsomething is crazy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:31.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,When I came home...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.77,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and heard that Shiina's work \Nwas going to be serialized,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.38,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I had been rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:38.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like my heart \Nwas going to shatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:40.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was serious about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:43.82,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hide from my \Nregrets or my frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:46.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But that's why it's so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:47.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You've just gotta do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:49.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to get rid of \Nthese feelings is to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:52.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I fail over and over, \NI just have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:55.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,When I thought of it that way, \NI started having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.67,0:21:58.55,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? \NYou're a masochist?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.55,0:22:00.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than being considered normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.76,0:22:02.63,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Spoken like a true resident of Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:04.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.07,0:22:10.52,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I like people who have goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:12.67,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I like people who try their hardest!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:13.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:16.30,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:19.28,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You two are too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:22.61,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's race to see who \Nreaches Sakura Hall first!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:23.90,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:26.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I'm starting in last place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:41.34,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you didn't bring...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:43.25,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,your underwear to the pool, Nanamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:44.81,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget that already, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:46.39,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,So future generations \Nwill remember this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:49.09,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,let's call this the No Panties \NNanamin fireworks welcome party!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:50.30,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call it that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:52.93,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't remember weird things!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:55.24,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It was just a little \Nrun without any underwear on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.86,0:22:58.89,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! No panties, \Nno life! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:01.77,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop saying "no panties."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.27,0:23:07.44,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:13.98,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.51,0:23:15.12,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:19.58,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I think I understand a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:21.79,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.60,0:23:34.38,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. I'm Rita, from England.
