Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:36.09,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Sukiyaki and sushi are delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:37.75,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:39.11,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll impersonate a boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.11,0:23:41.06,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you. Feel like flying north?
